title: Flying high - India launches record 104 satellites at one go | The Economic Times
text: India launches record 104 satellites at one go 1/11 Flying high Feb 15, 2017, 11.02 AM IST India created a world record on February 15, by successfully putting into orbit 104 satellites, including the country's own Cartosat-2earth observation satellite .
